reviewText: 3 wonderful movies all in one box.  LOVE it!
I'm happy with it. I would have gave my review five star but the clasp inside had broke.

three great movie musicals at a great price. I admit other than all being from MGM this is an odd combination but the price is so great it is hard to resist. This the DVD version not blu-ray and there are no extra's but the movies are so wonderful that all you have to do is sit back with your popcorn and enjoy
Nice combination of films that we have enjoyed through the years and are happy to now own :)
I can't wait to watch all 3 movies with my kids.
an unusual combination of movies but it works.  We have enjoyed all of them
Arrived on time, all movies included! Love
All classics and well made and acted, especially Fiddler on the Roof
These movies came in good quality! I absolutely loved this combo!
Three great movies for the price!

A very odd combination of movies. I bought it for "Chitty Chitty Bang Bang," having never seen "West Side Story" or "Fiddler on the Roof" anywhere but on stage. I was pleasantly surprised to enjoy them on my screen at home. Although there is very little these movies have in common (even the intended audiences are very different), I never sit to watch three movies in a row anyways. I really enjoy them all. All three have great and memorable music in them that is stuck in my head days after I see them.

Three of my all-time favourite movies in one collection.
I remember seeing Chitty Chitty Bang Bang when it first came out. And then only occasionally on broadcast TV years later full of commercials and cuts. Now my son can see it and he enjoys it as much as I do.
Fiddler on The Roof - always a classic, always brings a tear. Such a wonderful movie.
Great bargain.  Item exactly as promised.  Very easy transaction.
